{"tid":1124231,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"日本模型發燒友 砌崩壞了的元祖高達","createTime":"2019-04-25T02:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T13:50:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87ce48c3ff93986965adcb430c2d912af307daed","tid":1124231,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Tn5FiZNYieRei9OeXTtzbw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQyO2g9MzMw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/homerun/gameover.com.hk/35eab118570a2efb1a3779c1ba2a727b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTn5FiZNYieRei9OeXTtzbw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDQyO2g9MzMw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fhomerun%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F35eab118570a2efb1a3779c1ba2a727b&h=8d521a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幅《機動戰士Gundam》崩壞圖喺網絡世界都流傳咗好耐，相信大家都唔會陌生，眼窄、角短、頭成個頭盔咁，真係唔係人人頂得順。但偏偏，呢個世界就係有日本模型發燒友，真心Like呢隻這麼醜的元祖高達，仲專登將佢由2D變3D，好認真咁砌咗一隻頭大身細手短腳短嘅模型出嚟。成件事好有喜感，我笑咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RUV9dHf3NzJXZ7pIy7C1Mw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/homerun/gameover.com.hk/066008b1f303140f9fdc123e0a162bef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRUV9dHf3NzJXZ7pIy7C1Mw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fhomerun%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F066008b1f303140f9fdc123e0a162bef&h=609d8323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AGIDrsBYq5.Ael_qDELEeg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/homerun/gameover.com.hk/9acb343ed73c6b5db8ed6ece3fbd6110\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAGIDrsBYq5.Ael_qDELEeg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-H